# Connect Plus Activation Flow

## Default State
- "Get Started" CTA in Grow your Business grid → opens form popup

## Form Popup
- Checkbox consent → "Accept and Continue" CTA
- Uses consent card pattern (see `cards.mdc`)

## Loader Popup
- `type="loader"`, no close button
- Auto-dismisses after 6 seconds

## After Loader
- Opens new tab + sets enabled state on current page

## Enabled State
- Card moves from "Grow your Business" to "My Services" section
- Displayed with "Enabled" status chip + "Open Connect Plus" CTA
- Constrained to first-column width via `grid grid-cols-2 gap-6` wrapper
